scipy, numpy, and matplotlib are all used in the analysis tools and for figure
generation.

To "install", python setup.py build, and then copy the .so files from
build/lib. whatever to the main vdj directory

Also, you must copy vdjconfig to be .vdjconfig in your home directory. Adjust
the path to point to the correct directory.

or sudo python setup.py install to put into python tree

params.py must be updated upon install to point to the proper places

the bin directory must be added to the path for the scripts to work
